ndigo2-md.md)] include:"},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Trusted Root Certification Authorities<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[4415,4458],"source":"**Trusted Root Certification Authorities**."},{"content":"You can use the certificates in this store to create a chain of certificates, which can be traced back to a certification authority certificate in this store.","pos":[4459,4617]},{"pos":[4629,4942],"content":"[!IMPORTANT]\nThe local computer implicitly trusts any certificate placed in this store, even if the certificate does not come from a trusted third-party certification authority. For this reason, do not place any certificate into this store unless you fully trust the issuer and understand the consequences.","leadings":["","    >  "],"nodes":[{"content":"The local computer implicitly trusts any certificate placed in this store, even if the certificate does not come from a trusted third-party certification authority. For this reason, do not place any certificate into this store unless you fully trust the issuer and understand the consequences.","pos":[13,306],"nodes":[{"content":"The local computer implicitly trusts any certificate placed in this store, even if the certificate does not come from a trusted third-party certification authority.","pos":[0,164]},{"content":"For this reason, do not place any certificate into this store unless you fully trust the issuer and understand the consequences.","pos":[165,293]}]}]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Personal<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>.","pos":[4952,4965],"source":"**Personal**."},{"content":"This store is used for certificates associated with a user of a computer.","pos":[4966,5039]},{"content":"Typically this store is used for certificates issued by one of the certification authority certificates found in the Trusted Root Certification Authorities store.","pos":[5040,5202]},{"content":"Alternatively, a certificate found here may be self-issued and trusted by an application.","pos":[5203,5292]},{"pos":[5299,